sed overflow-hidden tap-highlight-transparent data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 text-tiny gap-2 rounded-small px-0 !gap-0 transition-transform-colors-opacity motion-reduce:transition-none bg-transparent text-default-foreground data-[hover=true]:bg-default/40 min-w-8 w-8 h-8" role="button" tabindex="0" target="_blank" title="Share on X" href="https://x.com/intent/post?text=Bloxd.io&url=https://www.bloxd.net"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" class="size-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="m17.687 3.063l-4.996 5.711l-4.32-5.711H2.112l7.477 9.776l-7.086 8.099h3.034l5.469-6.25l4.78 6.25h6.102l-7.794-10.304l6.625-7.571zm-1.064 16.06L5.654 4.782h1.803l10.846 14.34z"></path></svg></a><a class="z-0 group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center box-border appearance-none select-none whitespace-nowrap font-normal subpixel-antialiased overflow-hidden tap-highlight-transparent data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 text-tiny gap-2 rounded-small px-0 !gap-0 transition-transform-colors-opacity motion-reduce:transition-none bg-transparent text-default-foreground data-[hover=true]:bg-default/40 min-w-8 w-8 h-8" role="button" tabindex="0" target="_blank" title="Share on Reddit" href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https://www.bloxd.net&title=Bloxd.io"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" class="size-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M12.001 22c-5.523 0-10-4.477-10-10s4.477-10 10-10s10 4.477 10 10s-4.477 10-10 10m6.67-10a1.46 1.46 0 0 0-2.47-1a7.1 7.1 0 0 0-3.85-1.23l.65-3.12l2.14.45a1 1 0 1 0 .13-.61L12.821 6a.31.31 0 0 0-.37.24l-.74 3.47a7.14 7.14 0 0 0-3.9 1.23a1.46 1.46 0 1 0-1.61 2.39a3 3 0 0 0 0 .44c0 2.24 2.61 4.06 5.83 4.06s5.83-1.82 5.83-4.06a3 3 0 0 0 0-.44a1.46 1.46 0 0 0 .81-1.33m-10 1a1 1 0 1 1 2 0a1 1 0 0 1-2 0m5.81 2.75a3.84 3.84 0 0 1-2.47.77a3.84 3.84 0 0 1-2.47-.77a.27.27 0 0 1 .38-.38a3.27 3.27 0 0 0 2.08.63a3.28 3.28 0 0 0 2.09-.61a.28.28 0 1 1 .39.4zm-.18-1.71a1 1 0 1 1 1-1a1 1 0 0 1-1.01 1.04z"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class="ad-iframe-mb-4"><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-4755316476405316" data-ad-slot="3720634063" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins></div><div class="max-container w-full p-4"><h2 class="container-padding-x mb-2 text-center font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl">What is bloxd io</h2><p class="container-padding-x mt-4 whitespace-pre-line text-default-600 text-lg">bloxd io is a creative and exploratory Minecraft-like web game. Players can explore different worlds, build your dream land, and engage in adventures and battles</p></div><div class="max-container w-full p-4"><h2 class="container-padding-x text-center font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">How to play bloxd io</h2><div class=""><h3 class="container-padding-x mt-4 mb-4 font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">Controls</h3><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use WASD to move</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Shift + W to run</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use the space bar to jump</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use C or Z or Ctrl or Caps Lock to crouch</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use T or Enter to chat</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use O to open the menu</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use B to open the shop</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use left click to destroy blocks or use props</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use right click to place blocks</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use the mouse wheel or number keys to switch between props</p></div><div class=""><h3 class="container-padding-x mt-4 mb-4 font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">Commands</h3><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->Use / to start command</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->/rtv - Initiate a vote to switch maps, if the number of players is too low it will be switched directly</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->/players - Show players in the room</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->/played - Show current online length</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->/xp - Displays current level, experience and experience required to reach the next level</p><p class="mb-1 text-default-600 pl-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dot inline-block"><circle cx="12.1" cy="12.1" r="1"></circle></svg> <!-- -->/nobuffs - Remove all status/increases from yourself</p></div></div><div class="max-container w-full p-4"><h2 class="container-padding-x text-center font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">FAQ about bloxd io</h2><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-4"><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">Is bloxd io free?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">Yes, bloxd io is free.</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">Is bloxd io safe?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">Yes, bloxd io is safe. As of today, bloxd io has no reported privacy issues.</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">What devices can bloxd io be played on?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">Bloxd io can be played on any device that allows modern browsers, e.g. windows, mac, linux, chromebook, etc.</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">What age is bloxd io for?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">To use Bloxd.io, you must be at least 13 years old. If you are under 13, you need permission from a parent or guardian.</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">How to create a world in bloxd io?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">To create a World, click the Worlds game mode in the main Bloxd menu. Press "Create World". Choose a name for your World.</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">How do I add friends in bloxd io?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">You can add a friend by sending a friend request to anyone these ways

1. If a player chatting, click on his / her chatting and click Send Friend Request.
2. If his / her Accept the friend request, his / her will be your friend, but if his / her Decline the friend request, you can't be friend with his / her.</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden h-auto text-foreground box-border bg-content1 outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-focus data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-offset-2 shadow-none rounded-large data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 dark:data-[hover=true]:bg-content2 transition-transform-background motion-reduce:transition-none data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] tap-highlight-transparent cursor-pointer p-6" tabindex="0" role="button" data-open="false"><div class="flex-mid-y justify-between gap-2 font-bold text-xl"><div><h3 class="flex-1">Who made bloxd io?</h3></div><span style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;transform:rotate(0deg)"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-default-400"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14m-7-7v14"></path></svg></span></div><div style="opacity:0;height:0px;margin-top:0px"><span class="whitespace-pre-line text-left text-default-500">Arthur</span></div></div></div></div><div class="max-container w-full p-4"><h2 class="container-padding-x text-center font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">What game modes does bloxd io have</h2><a title="What game modes does bloxd io have" class="mt--2 mb-4 block w-full text-center text-default-400 transition-colors hover:text-primary" href="/en/game-mode">You can click here to see the details of the bloxd io's game mode.</a><div class="flex w-full flex-wrap gap-4"><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Survival</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Kill people (and do other things maybe) in a persistent open world</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Peaceful</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Mine, build, and explore in a persistent open world</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Creative</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Infinite blocks & flying in a persistent open world. Go build!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Factions</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Create, join, raid and trade with factions in a persistent open world</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Bedwars</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Destroy your enemies beds to win!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">One Block</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Start on a single block and build your island.</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Pirates</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Destroy your enemy's ship to win!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Greenville</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Build and upgrade your plot. Work for a living.</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Sky Wars</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Fight to death in the sky!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Cube Warfare</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Shoot your enemies and obtain cool powerups</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Infection</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Play as a Human trying to escape, or a Zombie trying to hunt them down!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Doodle Cube</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Build competitions with varied themes</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Bloxd Hop</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Jump your way through varied parkour maps</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Hide and Seek</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Hide as a block. Don't get caught!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Evil Tower</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Climb your way to the top of a randomly generated tower with absolutely no checkpoints</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Plots</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Build on your own plot of private land</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Murder Mystery</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Play as an innocent, detective or murderer!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Rocket Spleef</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Fire rockets and be the last one standing</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Bingo</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Craft Your Way to Bingo Glory!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Lucky Towers</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Put the odds in your favour to be the last player standing!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Rocket Obby</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Use rocket jumps to beat challenging maps</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">The Bridge</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">A 2v2 game. Jump into the other player's hole to win!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Paintball</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Paint the town redâ¦ or whatever color you'd like!</p></div><div class="w-full rounded-lg bg-content1 p-4 md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33%-0.5rem)]"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Worlds</h3><p class="mt-4 text-default-500">Create your own world</p></div></div></div><div class="max-container w-full p-4 flex-mid-xy flex-col"><h2 class="container-padding-x mb-2 text-center font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl">Play bloxd io Now!</h2><p class="container-padding-x mt-4 whitespace-pre-line text-default-600 text-lg text-center">Start your adventure in bloxd io, a creative and exploratory Minecraft-like web game. Players can explore different worlds, build your dream land, and engage in adventures and battles.</p><button class="z-0 group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center box-border appearance-none select-none whitespace-nowrap font-normal subpixel-antialiased overflow-hidden tap-highlight-transparent data-[pressed=true]:scale-[0.97] outline-none data-[focus-visible=true]:z-10 data-[focus-visible=true]:outline-2 data-