ildren\":\"You can click here to see the details of the bloxd io's game mode.\"}]\n4:[\"$\",\"html\",null,{\"lang\":\"en\",\"className\":\"dark\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"body\",null,{\"className\":\"dark flex min-h-screen flex-col bg-background font-sans text-foreground antialiased __variable_6bee3b\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L18\",null,{\"color\":\"var(--colors-primary)\"}],\"$L19\",[\"$\",\"$L1a\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"$L1b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"$L1c\",null,{}]]}]}]\n1e:T5a8,In this mode, there are three professions, namely: killer, detective, and civilian. Among them, Detective and Civilian are one camp.\nHere, everyone has a different armor color (used to identify different players). Bystanders and players use two different chatbars (player chatbars can't see bystander's messages). Surviving players can get a gun (TAR-21, can only be fired once) for killing murderers after collecting 10 Moonstones. Gold is awarded for completing the mission.\nThe killer will get his weapon 5 seconds after the game starts and his mission is to kill everyone before the countdown ends. They can also pick up moonstones to camouflage themselves and can buy other murder weapons in the store.\nKiller camp victory condition: death of all detectives and civilians\n\nThe detective carries his own firearm (M16, which can be fired once every 5 seconds), and his mission is to find and kill the detective with the gun in his hand. Being killed by an assassin, being accidentally killed by a civilian (who has a gun), or accidentally killing a civilian will cause the gun to fall out of his hand and he will die.\nA civilian who accidentally kills the detective will die and the gun will not be dropped. Interestingly, the Detective camp drops a relic when they die and can purchase items such as relics with gold.\n\nDetective camp victory condition: the killer dies, or there are still civilians or detectives alive before the countdown ends19:[\"$\",\"$L1d\",null,{\"locale\":\"en\",\"now\":\"$D2026-03-24T20:43:33.548Z\",\"timeZone\":\"UTC\",\"messages\":{\"web\":{\"404\":{\"title\":\"404\",\"desc\":\"Page not found\"},\"menu\":{\"common\":{\"privacy\":\"Privacy Policy\",\"terms\":\"Terms and Conditions\"}},\"error\":{\"defaultError\":\"Oops... An error occurred\",\"networkError\":\"Network error\"},\"message\":{\"submitSuccess\":\"Submission successful\",\"editSuccess\":\"Edit successful\"},\"actions\":{\"back\":\"Back\",\"cancel\":\"Cancel\",\"ok\":\"OK\",\"backHome\":\"Back to Homepage\",\"login\":\"Login\",\"loginOrRegister\":\"Login / Register\",\"logout\":\"Logout\",\"dashboard\":\"User Center\",\"submit\":\"Submit\",\"upgrade\":\"Upgrade\",\"refresh\":\"Refresh\",\"startNow\":\"Start Now\"},\"components\":{\"toc\":{\"title\":\"Table of Contents\"},\"codeSender\":{\"button\":\"Get\",\"errorMsg\":\"Failed to get verification code, please try again later.\"},\"table\":{\"emptyContent\":\"No content available\"}},\"terms\":{\"desc\":\"This page describes our terms and conditions\"},\"privacy\":{\"desc\":\"We take your privacy seriously. Explore our comprehensive privacy policy and learn how we safeguard your data\"}},\"game\":{\"seo\":{\"name\":\"Bloxd.io\",\"title\":\"%s | Play \u003cgame\u003e\u003c/game\u003e Online for Free on PC \u0026 Mobile\",\"desc\":\"bloxd io is a creative and exploratory Minecraft-like web game. Players can explore different worlds, build your dream land, and engage in adventures and battles\"},\"game\":{\"what\":{\"title\":\"What is bloxd io\",\"desc\":\"bloxd io is a creative and exploratory Minecraft-like web game. Players can explore different worlds, build your dream land, and engage in adventures and battles\"},\"how\":{\"title\":\"How to play bloxd io\",\"control\":{\"title\":\"Controls\",\"desc\":{\"1\":\"Use WASD to move\",\"2\":\"Shift + W to run\",\"3\":\"Use the space bar to jump\",\"4\":\"Use C or Z or Ctrl or Caps Lock to crouch\",\"5\":\"Use T or Enter to chat\",\"6\":\"Use O to open the menu\",\"7\":\"Use B to open the shop\",\"8\":\"Use left click to destroy blocks or use props\",\"9\":\"Use right click to place blocks\",\"10\":\"Use the mouse wheel or number keys to switch between props\"}},\""])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"command\":{\"title\":\"Commands\",\"desc\":{\"1\":\"Use / to start command\",\"2\":\"/rtv - Initiate a vote to switch maps, if the number of players is too low it will be switched directly\",\"3\":\"/players - Show players in the room\",\"4\":\"/played - Show current online length\",\"5\":\"/xp - Displays current level, experience and experience required to reach the next level\",\"6\":\"/nobuffs - Remove all status/increases from yourself\"}}},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"FAQ about bloxd io\",\"items\":{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Is bloxd io free?\",\"desc\":\"Yes, bloxd io is free.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Is bloxd io safe?\",\"desc\":\"Yes, bloxd io is safe. As of today, bloxd io has no reported privacy issues.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"What devices can bloxd io be played on?\",\"desc\":\"Bloxd io can be played on any device that allows modern browsers, e.g. windows, mac, linux, chromebook, etc.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"What age is bloxd io for?\",\"desc\":\"To use Bloxd.io, you must be at least 13 years old. If you are under 13, you need permission from a parent or guardian.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"How to create a world in bloxd io?\",\"desc\":\"To create a World, click the Worlds game mode in the main Bloxd menu. Press \\\"Create World\\\". Choose a name for your World.\"},\"6\":{\"title\":\"How do I add friends in bloxd io?\",\"desc\":\"You can add a friend by sending a friend request to anyone these ways\\n\\n1. If a player chatting, click on his / her chatting and click Send Friend Request.\\n2. If his / her Accept the friend request, his / her will be your friend, but if his / her Decline the friend request, you can't be friend with his / her.\"},\"7\":{\"title\":\"Who made bloxd io?\",\"desc\":\"Arthur\"}}},\"mode\":{\"title\":\"What game modes does bloxd io have\",\"items\":{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Survival\",\"subtitle\":\"Kill people (and do other things maybe) in a persistent open world\",\"desc\":\"This mode is a basic survival mode with mechanics such as health points, combat and synthesis. The only difference between it and Peace Mode is the additional combat system (attack props and blood)\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Peaceful\",\"subtitle\":\"Mine, build, and explore in a persistent open world\",\"desc\":\"All the player has to do is mine, build, and explore within an open world. There is no combat system in this mode and characters have no blood, similar to Creative Mode in this regard.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Creative\",\"subtitle\":\"Infinite blocks \u0026 flying in a persistent open world. Go build!\",\"desc\":\"In this mode, players can fly and take unlimited items.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Factions\",\"subtitle\":\"Create, join, raid and trade with factions in a persistent open world\",\"desc\":\"In this mode, players have the option to create (costing 50 gold coins)/join a faction (Faction) and hold different positions in the faction.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Bedwars\",\"subtitle\":\"Destroy your enemies beds to win!\",\"desc\":\"Get Up War is divided into two-player mode, one-player mode and four-player team mode.\\nUse the resources in the map's resource points to buy items and do your best to guard your bed! Tear down your opponents' beds and turn them into cold corpses!\"},\"6\":{\"title\":\"One Block\",\"subtitle\":\"Start on a single block and build your island.\",\"desc\":\"In this mode, you will be born on an island with âonly one squareâ.\\nBy constantly digging underneath your feet for square 1, you will gradually get more and better squares, and use this square as a base to build a home.\\nWhen you have dug enough squares, you will move on to the next stage. Once you have unlocked all the stages, you are free to choose the current stage in order to obtain cubes.\\nThe mode also has a âskill pointâ setting, so when you dig up a specific cube, a skill corresponding to that cube will be discovered in the skill tree.\"},\"7\":{\"title\":\"Pirates\",\"subtitle\":\"Destroy your enemy's ship to win!\",\"desc\":\"In Pirate Battle, players are randomly divided into two or four teams. Players need to find a way to destroy the enemy's birth point and kill them.\"},\"8\":{\"title\":\"Greenville\",\"subtitle\":\"Build and upgrade your plot. Work for a living.\",\"desc\":\"Greenville mode, peaceful (except in areas where PvP is allowed). There are two parts: the residential ar"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"ea and the square. Players settle in the residential area and earn currency in the plaza.\"},\"9\":{\"title\":\"Sky Wars\",\"subtitle\":\"Fight to death in the sky!\",\"desc\":\"In this mode, players need to find ways to kill all opponents using resources available on empty islands within the map in order to win. Choose a profession (enabled in-game by pressing the B button) to get unique items and weapons at the beginning of the game.\"},\"10\":{\"title\":\"Cube Warfare\",\"subtitle\":\"Shoot your enemies and obtain cool powerups\",\"desc\":\"This mode is one of the four classic modes, in this game mode you will be born in three rotating maps.\\nEach game lasts for 10 minutes, and when the time is up the game will switch maps and reset the player's status.\\nIn its multiplayer mode, players will be divided into red/blue teams, and the team score is the sum of the scores of the players on the team.\\nThis mode has Streak Points and Golds. Damage you inflict on other players is converted into points, which are zeroed out by death and game over, and they are used to purchase increases within the round; for every player you kill, you earn a gold coin, which is only reduced by purchases and is a tool for unlocking options.\"},\"11\":{\"title\":\"Infection\",\"subtitle\":\"Play as a Human trying to escape, or a Zombie trying to hunt them down!\",\"desc\":\"In this mode, players are divided into two camps, Human and Zombie, each with different suits.\\nHumans need to escape the map before they are wiped out by the Zombies, and they can upgrade their weapons/unlock gates with points earned from hitting/killing Zombies.\\nZombies need to infect all humans before they escape the map, and killing humans will turn them into zombies.\"},\"12\":{\"title\":\"Doodle Cube\",\"subtitle\":\"Build competitions with varied themes\",\"desc\":\"Players need to build a building with a specified theme in a limited amount of time, and ultimately all the rest of the players present will vote on who built the best, in both single and two-player modes.\"},\"13\":{\"title\":\"Bloxd Hop\",\"subtitle\":\"Jump your way through varied parkour maps\",\"desc\":\"Players need to run and jump from square to square to reach the final destination!\"},\"14\":{\"title\":\"Hide and Seek\",\"subtitle\":\"Hide as a block. Don't get caught!\",\"desc\":\"The Hider can choose to turn into a type of square with its own crash box, and after staying in one location for 5 seconds it will automatically hide the player's name and align itself with the square next to it, at which point the character has a hit decision of the same size as the object block. Hiders will automatically turn into captors when they are killed by captors. The Hider's job is to hide himself and not be killed by the Captor before the countdown ends.\\nCaptors are spawned with a gold sword, a diamond helmet and a pair of diamond boots, and their task is to find and kill all hiders before the countdown ends.\"},\"15\":{\"title\":\"Evil Tower\",\"subtitle\":\"Climb your way to the top of a randomly generated tower with absolutely no checkpoints\",\"desc\":\"The player needs to get to the top of the tower. There are many traps (red squares) in the process, and stepping on them will teleport you back to your birth point (or a purchased archive). Purchasing skills will allow you to escape this evil tower more quickly.\"},\"16\":{\"title\":\"Plots\",\"subtitle\":\"Build on your own plot of private land\",\"desc\":\"Here, you only need to build your buildings on your stronghold. There is no voting system or time limit.\"},\"17\":{\"title\":\"Murder Mystery\",\"subtitle\":\"Play as an innocent, detective or murderer!\",\"desc\":\"$1e\"},\"18\":{\"title\":\"Rocket Spleef\",\"subtitle\":\"Fire rockets and be the last one standing\",\"desc\":\"Blast others into the void with your RPG to win.\"},\"19\":{\"title\":\"Bingo\",\"subtitle\":\"Craft Your Way to Bingo Glory!\",\"desc\":\"Players are divided into teams and the first team to synthesize/get all the quest items will win.\"},\"20\":{\"title\":\"Lucky Towers\",\"subtitle\":\"Put the odds in your favour to be the last player standing!\",\"desc\":\"In the game, the player will be spread out over many one-grid columns, and the playe"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"r will be randomly given items/object blocks to prevent dropping them\"},\"21\":{\"title\":\"Rocket Obby\",\"subtitle\":\"Use rocket jumps to beat challenging maps\",\"desc\":\"Parkour through RPG bombing, with different wool having different effects.\"},\"22\":{\"title\":\"The Bridge\",\"subtitle\":\"A 2v2 game. Jump into the other player's hole to win!\",\"desc\":\"There are red/blue teams of 2 players each. Players need to find a way to jump through a one square wide bridge into a hole in the opposing team's base in order to win, and the characters are spawned with a certain number of cubes, pickaxes, iron swords, and armor.\"},\"23\":{\"title\":\"Paintball\",\"subtitle\":\"Paint the town redâ¦ or whatever color you'd like!\",\"desc\":\"Players are divided into four teams (random colors) and use props in their hands to color the map in a fixed map, and the team with the largest percentage of coloring at the end wins.\"},\"24\":{\"title\":\"Worlds\",\"subtitle\":\"Create your own world\",\"desc\":\"Rooms created and managed by players.The owner can use commands that are not available to normal players.\"}}},\"cta\":{\"title\":\"Play bloxd io Now!\",\"desc\":\"Start your adventure in bloxd io, a creative and exploratory Minecraft-like web game. Players can explore different worlds, build your dream land, and engage in adventures and battles.\"}},\"gameMode\":{\"title\":\"Game Mode\",\"desc\":\"This page describes how many game modes bloxd io has, their respective names and their profiles. Each game mode is very interesting and worth trying!\",\"seeDetail\":\"You can click here to see the details of the bloxd io's game mode.\"}}},\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1f\",null,{\"locale\":\"en\",\"className\":\"flex flex-grow-[1] flex-col\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"attribute\":\"class\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"segmentPath\":[\"children\",\"$0:f:0:1:2:children:0\",\"children\"],\"error\":\"$undefined\",\"errorStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"errorScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}],\"templateStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"templateScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"notFound\":[[],\"$L21\"],\"forbidden\":\"$undefined\",\"unauthorized\":\"$undefined\"}],[\"$\",\"$L22\",null,{}]]}]}]}]\nc:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\na:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"title\",\"1\",{\"children\":\"Bloxd.io | Play Bloxd.io Online for Free on PC \u0026 Mobile\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"bloxd io is a creative and exploratory Minecraft-like web game. Players can explore different worlds, build your dream land, and engage in adventures and battles\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"name\":\"robots\",\"content\":\"index\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"4\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://www.bloxd.net\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"5\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"en\",\"href\":\"https://www.bloxd.net\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"6\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"es\",\"href\":\"h